name: Grafflower
description:
Graffiti / Flower = Grafflowers

This piece is to gift to others, the idea is not to hold but to distribute, like a congrats bouquet or that of a gift. 
Influenced by my background in graffiti, I wanted to make a piece that is a digital representation in my style of painting. 
It's a project in the early stages that purpose is to distribute to others.
